textBeforeTable: Related companies Great Wolf Resorts Holdings Inc is a United States-based company, which operates a family of indoor waterpark resorts. The Company owns and operates its family resorts under the Great Wolf Lodge brand. Great Wolf Lodge offers a range of amenities that includes suites; entertainment areas, with entertainments ranging from Northern Lights arcades to MagiQuest action adventure game; resort activities, ranging from Storytime around the fireplace to edu-tainment activities in the Cub Club children’s activity areas; an Elements Spa for adults; Scooops, a special children’s spa with ice cream manicures and pedicures, and a fitness center. The Company's Great Wolf Lodge resorts are located in Wisconsin Dells, Wisconsin; Sandusky, Ohio; Traverse City, Michigan; Kansas City, Kansas; Williamsburg, Virginia; the Pocono Mountains, Pennsylvania; Niagara Falls, Ontario; Mason, Ohio; Grapevine, Texas; Grand Mound, Washington; Concord, North Carolina, and New England/Boston, Massachusetts.
